application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Outline application, with access only to be considered in detail, for the redevelopment of part of the Orchard Hill site to provide up to 246 dwellings in a range of two and three storey buildings, a Class A1 retail unit, togather with alterations to Fountain Drive, the laying out of internal access roads and formation of a new secondary access road across the former BIBRA site from Woodmansterne Road.
